STATE
v.
Donald Ray WILLIAMS. No. 519P05. Supreme Court of North Carolina. November 3, 2005. William P. Hart, Special Deputy Attorney General, Clark Everett, District Attorney, for State.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 12th day of September 2005 by Defendant for "Petition for Writ of Certiorari":

"Motion Dismissed by order of the Court in conference this the 3rd day of November 2005."
